  <description>
    <p>
      Parcel Buddy lets you track parcels from a wide range of carriers with a clean, visual interface.
      Get real-time updates and notifications for your packages, all in one place.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Support for multiple carriers</li>
      <li>Real-time tracking updates</li>
      <li>Custom notifications for delivery status changes</li>
      <li>Self-hostable solution for privacy-conscious users</li>
      <li>Intuitive and user-friendly interface</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Parcel Buddy makes it easy to stay on top of your deliveries.
    </p>
  </description>

